         <abstract id="aspace_e16a25cda74f136db5ee074ec7c6ee70">The materials consist of photographs and slides documenting the construction of Silliman College at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views and photographs of the master's house.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_5ca6d14ce6cd9960edbfd24d7e103221">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_c35ec940f583273b4075e3f2259a7f8d">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Silliman College, Yale University, Photographs (RU 601). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_5003a7a392970ae11aa59fb4b920489c">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b862060123447efe9b78fdcb702e8a93">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The materials are arranged in four series: I. Construction Progress Photographs, 1939-1940. II. General Views, 1939-1940. III. Oversize. IV. Slides and transparencies; folio.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_7387977ada7afd6f7e3a04de2b7403b9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs and slides documenting the construction of Silliman College at Yale. Included are interior and exterior views and photographs of the master's house.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
